          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "謝謝你。#p3001003# 等一下。#b#t4033417##k 10個、#b#t4033421##k十個。"
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "快去吧！#b#m401010100##k、 #b#m401020000##k。去狩獵吧！"
